      "block_name": "lumo/ld-hero",
      "title": "Lumo Dental — Hero",
      "html_template": "<section style=\"background:#FAF8F4;padding:100px 24px 80px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"max-width:74rem;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:72px;align-items:center;\"><div><p style=\"font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8A26A;margin:0 0 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;\"><span style=\"width:24px;height:1px;background:#C8A26A;display:inline-block;\"></span>Östermalm · Stockholm</p><h1 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,5vw,4.8rem);font-weight:700;color:#13201D;line-height:1.02;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;\">Tandvård<br>som lyser<br>inifrån.</h1><p style=\"font-size:1.05rem;color:#6D6A67;line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 44px;max-width:420px;\">Precision, omtanke och resultat som varar. Vi tar hand om ditt leende med samma noggrannhet du förväntar dig av Stockholms bästa klinik.</p><div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;\"><a href=\"#boka\" style=\"background:#2C574A;color:#ffffff;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;padding:15px 34px;border-radius:50px;text-decoration:none;\">Boka din tid →</a><a href=\"#behandlingar\" style=\"color:#13201D;font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid #13201D;padding-bottom:2px;\">Se behandlingar</a></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:36px;margin-top:56px;padding-top:40px;border-top:1px solid #E8E3DB;\"><div><p style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:1.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#13201D;margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1;\">2 000+</p><p style=\"font-size:0.72rem;color:#A09C99;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">Nöjda patienter</p></div><div style=\"width:1px;background:#E8E3DB;\"></div><div><p style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:1.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#13201D;margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1;\">4.9 ★</p><p style=\"font-size:0.72rem;color:#A09C99;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">Google-betyg</p></div><div style=\"width:1px;background:#E8E3DB;\"></div><div><p style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:1.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#13201D;margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1;\">15 år</p><p style=\"font-size:0.72rem;color:#A09C99;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">I branschen</p></div></div></div><div style=\"position:relative;height:640px;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:28px;overflow:hidden;\"><img src=\"https://placehold.co/800x900/D8D2C8/2C574A\" alt=\"Lumo Dental\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;\"></div><div style=\"position:absolute;top:28px;right:-16px;background:#13201D;border-radius:14px;padding:16px 22px;\"><p style=\"font-size:0.66rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);margin:0 0 5px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;\">Nästa lediga tid</p><p style=\"font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:#C8A26A;margin:0;\">I morgon · 09:30</p></div><div style=\"position:absolute;bottom:32px;left:-16px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;padding:18px 22px;box-shadow:0 12px 48px rgba(19,32,29,0.14);\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;background:#F0EDE7;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.1rem;\">✦</div><div><p style=\"font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:600;color:#13201D;margin:0 0 2px;\">Certifierad klinik</p><p style=\"font-size:0.75rem;color:#A09C99;margin:0;\">Socialstyrelsen godkänd</p></div></div></div></div></div></section>",
      "schema": []
