      "html_template": "<section id=\"boka\" style=\"background:#13201D;padding:110px 24px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:700px;height:700px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(44,87,74,0.35) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;\"></div><div style=\"max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;position:relative;\"><p style=\"font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8A26A;margin:0 0 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;\"><span style=\"width:24px;height:1px;background:#C8A26A;display:inline-block;\"></span>Boka din tid<span style=\"width:24px;height:1px;background:#C8A26A;display:inline-block;\"></span></p><h2 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.2rem);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-0.02em;\">Ditt leende<br>börjar här.</h2><p style=\"font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);line-height:1.8;margin:0 auto 48px;max-width:460px;\">Ta steget mot friskare tänder och ett starkare självförtroende. Boka din kostnadsfria konsultation i dag.</p><div style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"background:#C8A26A;color:#13201D;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;padding:16px 40px;border-radius:50px;text-decoration:none;\">Boka kostnadsfri konsultation</a><a href=\"tel:085511235\" style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);color:#ffffff;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;padding:16px 32px;border-radius:50px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);\">08-551 123 45</a></div><p style=\"font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.28);margin:28px 0 0;\">Öppet Mån–Fre 08–18 · Lör 09–14 · Strandvägen 7, Östermalm</p></div></section>",
